Lord Gongye.

298
00:17:49,910 --> 00:17:50,640
You are

299
00:17:50,890 --> 00:17:52,619
the county magistrate, Tumen.

300
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:55,930
Mr. Xi, you have a good eye.

301
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:58,380
I'm a little older than Tumen.

302
00:17:58,589 --> 00:17:59,490
Whenever we meet someone new,

303
00:17:59,490 --> 00:18:01,560
most people would mistake me for the county magistrate.

304
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:03,540
I do business in Yazhou

305
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:06,430
and often come into contact with officials.

306
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:07,990
As such, I learned a trick or two

307
00:18:07,990 --> 00:18:10,050
about observing and reading people.

308
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:11,230
It's nothing much.

309
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:15,110
Mr. Xi, you spoke your judgment

310
00:18:15,110 --> 00:18:16,990
without hesitation.

311
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:18,900
Your thoughts and certainty

312
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:21,060
are different from ordinary people.

313
00:18:21,790 --> 00:18:23,320
If I weren't brave enough,

314
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:24,970
I would not have come all the way

315
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:26,470
to do business in Heman.

316
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,040
Don't you agree?

317
00:18:39,740 --> 00:18:40,510
She said she would

318
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:42,240
never mention the tribe again.

319
00:18:42,450 --> 00:18:44,450
But isn't she always mentioning it?

320
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:49,300
Is it over?

321
00:18:51,950 --> 00:18:52,650
Madam.

322
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:55,360
What did you do today?

323
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,690
This is a toxic oath.

324
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:00,400
A toxic oath?

325
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:03,510
I've vowed to live and die with my husband.

326
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,970
So I set up the altar to make the oath tonight.

327
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:17,960
Mr. Xi, so you're

328
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:19,950
General Nan's distant cousin.

329
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:23,390
You're here to do tea business?

330
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:25,230
Yes.

331
00:19:25,910 --> 00:19:27,670
Yazhou is a place for the demoted.

332
00:19:27,670 --> 00:19:29,590
Those old ex-officials

333
00:19:29,870 --> 00:19:32,270
can't get used to a downgrade in lifestyle.

334
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:33,510
Good wine and tea

335
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:34,970
are essential to them.

336
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:37,180
All the flower tea businesses in the county

337
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,780
are under the Gongye family.

338
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:40,720
I'll let you in on the business.

339
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:45,210
Then I'll drink tea instead of wine

340
00:19:45,430 --> 00:19:46,890
to thank you, Lord Gongye.

341
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:53,100
On the 13th of last month,

342
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:56,150
two people died accidentally in the city.

343
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:58,550
It seems to have implicated you.

344
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:00,830
What happened?

345
00:20:01,780 --> 00:20:02,780
About that...

346
00:20:05,270 --> 00:20:07,130
That was my first day in Heman.

347
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:08,470
I met two people

348
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:10,100
who claimed to be tea merchants.

349
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:12,710
They said they wanted to show me some tea leaves.

350
00:20:12,710 --> 00:20:13,550
In the end,

351
00:20:14,110 --> 00:20:15,950
they showed me Zornia.

352
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,370
There was a miscommunication between us

353
00:20:20,370 --> 00:20:22,470
which resulted in a misunderstanding.

354
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:23,110
Later,

355
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:24,500
those two

356
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:26,230
mysteriously died.

357
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:27,750
It made me

358
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,070
really helpless.

359
00:20:33,510 --> 00:20:34,510
I see.

360
00:20:34,950 --> 00:20:35,510
Yes.

361
00:20:36,230 --> 00:20:37,240
I was scared,

362
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,880
so I left the city to hide for a few days.

363
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,360
But I didn't know the way

364
00:20:41,870 --> 00:20:43,930
and accidentally entered a village.

365
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:46,910
Somehow, I ended up

366
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:48,750
burning their field.

367
00:20:49,110 --> 00:20:50,910
After that, I found out

368
00:20:51,470 --> 00:20:53,030
that it was a Zornia field.

369
00:20:55,910 --> 00:20:56,770
Don't you think

370
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:58,190
it's funny?

371
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:12,390
Is it that funny?

372
00:21:29,190 --> 00:21:29,910
Dr. Yan,

373
00:21:30,470 --> 00:21:31,550
what are you doing?

374
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:33,860
I'm setting up a trap.

375
00:21:34,590 --> 00:21:35,070
Madam.

376
00:21:35,390 --> 00:21:36,760
Don't touch this powder.

377
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:37,690
It's poisonous.

378
00:21:38,230 --> 00:21:38,910
Do you know what is

379
00:21:38,910 --> 00:21:40,040
happening tonight?

380
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:43,230
I know.

381
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,800
They want to take us hostage

382
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:46,870
and use us to threaten Mr. Xi

383
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:47,800
and General Nan.

384
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:49,400
Madam, don't worry.

385
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,910
I won't let them succeed.

386
00:22:13,910 --> 00:22:15,630
What a beautiful night

387
00:22:15,820 --> 00:22:17,020
for murder.

388
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:53,040
Dr. Yan.

389
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:53,870
What’s going on outside?

390
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:54,670
Don't be afraid, Madam.

391
00:22:54,670 --> 00:22:55,470
It'll be fine.

392
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,710
Everything will be fine.

393
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:57,390
I'll stay here.

394
00:22:57,390 --> 00:22:58,230
You go in first.

395
00:22:58,230 --> 00:22:58,830
Go.

396
00:22:59,110 --> 00:22:59,710
Go.

397
00:23:12,830 --> 00:23:13,630
Jiang Xinbai.

398
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:16,000
You must come back safely.

399
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:31,210
Why did the music stop?

400
00:23:31,910 --> 00:23:32,710
Keep playing.

401
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:33,780
Continue.

402
00:23:35,150 --> 00:23:35,710
Dance.

403
00:23:39,290 --> 00:23:41,490
Why are you serving tea for General Nan?

404
00:23:41,650 --> 00:23:42,650
Where's the wine?

405
00:23:44,470 --> 00:23:45,550
To be honest,

406
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,240
an assassin attacked me a few days ago.

407
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:51,990
I almost died.

408
00:23:52,510 --> 00:23:54,440
Luckily, my cousin risked his life

409
00:23:54,840 --> 00:23:55,950
to save me.

410
00:23:56,730 --> 00:23:58,660
The wound has recovered recently.

411
00:23:58,830 --> 00:24:00,350
I can't drink these days.

412
00:24:02,370 --> 00:24:03,610
That happened?

413
00:24:04,310 --> 00:24:05,300
Haven't you

414
00:24:05,870 --> 00:24:06,830
heard about it?

415
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:09,950
I did not know.

416
00:24:10,910 --> 00:24:12,390
Did you catch the assassin?

417
00:24:12,390 --> 00:24:14,850
He committed suicide to escape punishment.

418
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:16,800
Did you

419
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:18,550
offend someone?

420
00:24:19,190 --> 00:24:21,190
Do you remember?

421
00:24:22,390 --> 00:24:23,310
One year ago,

422
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:24,670
I sent

423
00:24:25,170 --> 00:24:27,800
five trusted subordinates

424
00:24:28,070 --> 00:24:29,830
into the heart of danger.

425
00:24:30,710 --> 00:24:32,750
They were all brutally killed.

426
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:34,590
It was thanks to you two

427
00:24:34,590 --> 00:24:36,710
that my men's bodies were recovered.

428
00:24:38,050 --> 00:24:38,920
This year,

429
00:24:39,510 --> 00:24:41,170
I dreamed of them every night.

430
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:44,510
They asked me to avenge them.

431
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:11,790
The Zornia crisis is severe in Heman.

432
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:13,240
Who is the biggest force driving it?

433
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:15,040
Who is the mastermind behind it?

434
00:25:15,070 --> 00:25:15,830
My lords,

435
00:25:17,110 --> 00:25:17,630
don't you

436
00:25:17,630 --> 00:25:19,030
want to know the truth?

437
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:22,180
General Nan.

438
00:25:22,430 --> 00:25:24,190
You're drunk before you drink.

439
00:25:24,870 --> 00:25:27,270
Today's party is for us old friends to meet.

440
00:25:27,510 --> 00:25:29,070
The people of the past are gone.

441
00:25:29,070 --> 00:25:31,230
General, please look ahead

442
00:25:32,430 --> 00:25:34,360
and cherish the people around you.

443
00:25:36,910 --> 00:25:37,670
Cousin.

444
00:25:40,190 --> 00:25:42,320
Don't make things difficult for them.

445
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:45,150
Actually,

446
00:25:46,430 --> 00:25:48,310
Lord Gongye and Lord Tumen

447
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,830
are also at their superior's disposal.

448
00:25:50,830 --> 00:25:51,920
There are many things

449
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:53,520
they have no power to decide.

450
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,980
If we have important questions,

451
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,910
why don't we ask the real master?

452
00:26:01,150 --> 00:26:01,870
Right?

453
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:04,990
Mr. Moqi?

454
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:15,270
Or should I call you

455
00:26:15,750 --> 00:26:17,020
Ms. Moqi?

456
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:45,430
[Moqi]

457
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:55,400
You were very careful.

458
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:58,160
But you forgot to disguise your hands.

459
00:26:58,470 --> 00:27:00,070
It's an important occasion,

460
00:27:00,180 --> 00:27:01,390
but a woman managed to disguise

461
00:27:01,390 --> 00:27:03,470
herself as a male musician and mix into the venue.

462
00:27:03,470 --> 00:27:04,640
Apart from Ms. Moqi,

463
00:27:05,150 --> 00:27:06,750
I can't think of anyone else.

464
00:27:08,110 --> 00:27:09,790
Plus, my cousin once said

465
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:12,790
he had never seen the master of the Moqi family in person.

466
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:13,670
I wondered

467
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,650
if that was because

468
00:27:15,950 --> 00:27:17,550
the master of the Moqi family

469
00:27:18,030 --> 00:27:19,000
was a lady.

470
00:27:22,630 --> 00:27:23,670
Mr. Xi.

471
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:25,230
You have sharp eyes.

472
00:27:27,500 --> 00:27:28,630
It's been a few days.

473
00:27:29,310 --> 00:27:30,910
You look better than before.

474
00:27:31,170 --> 00:27:31,920
Who is she?

475
00:27:32,710 --> 00:27:33,910
When did she see me?

476
00:27:38,670 --> 00:27:39,800
You know each other?

477
00:27:40,430 --> 00:27:41,420
Not only does Mr. Xi

478
00:27:41,420 --> 00:27:43,320
know Ms. Moqi,

479
00:27:43,430 --> 00:27:45,070
they go way back.

480
00:27:50,990 --> 00:27:52,190
What's wrong, Mr. Xi?

481
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:54,750
Don't you recognize me?

482
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:57,370
Who was she?

483
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,430
So you're the

484
00:28:03,460 --> 00:28:05,660
female doctor giving free treatment.

485
00:28:07,470 --> 00:28:08,070
It's her.

486
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:11,710
Mr. Xi, I've checked.

487
00:28:11,710 --> 00:28:13,240
There's no ambush outside.

488
00:28:20,350 --> 00:28:21,630
Whose side are you on?

489
00:28:24,190 --> 00:28:25,270
Right back at you.

490
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:26,540
Nan Jifeng.

491
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,070
Aren't all the water transport in Heman

492
00:28:28,070 --> 00:28:29,200
under your control?

493
00:28:30,150 --> 00:28:31,830
Why was the pleasure boat I rented

494
00:28:31,830 --> 00:28:33,690
under the Moqi family's control?

495
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:36,230
Whose side are you on?

496
00:28:37,430 --> 00:28:38,470
What do you mean?

497
00:28:41,950 --> 00:28:43,950
Are you pretending or are you actually stupid?

498
00:28:43,950 --> 00:28:45,160
Ms. Moqi

499
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:47,070
owns the pleasure boat I rented.

500
00:28:48,670 --> 00:28:49,420
I think

501
00:28:49,470 --> 00:28:51,800
all the pleasure boat businesses in Heman

502
00:28:51,870 --> 00:28:53,510
should be under her name.

503
00:28:57,360 --> 00:28:58,310
Just now,

504
00:28:58,950 --> 00:29:00,410
you were silent for so long

505
00:29:00,590 --> 00:29:02,030
because you were thinking about that?

506
00:29:02,030 --> 00:29:02,750
What else?

507
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:06,230
So,

508
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:08,720
since my first day

509
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:09,510
in Heman,

510
00:29:09,950 --> 00:29:10,880
Ms. Moqi

511
00:29:11,070 --> 00:29:12,600
has had her eyes on me.

512
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:16,470
You're exaggerating.

513
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:19,140
A new guest is here in Heman.

514
00:29:19,990 --> 00:29:22,020
As the host, I must do my part.

515
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,110
I just didn't expect

516
00:29:23,110 --> 00:29:24,670
you to be so rude.

517
00:29:25,030 --> 00:29:26,510
You killed two of my men

518
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:28,430
at the first sign of conflict

519
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:30,180
and burned my fields.

520
00:29:32,190 --> 00:29:33,190
Sorry about that.

521
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,900
The ignorant is innocent.

522
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:38,390
From today onwards, as long as

523
00:29:39,430 --> 00:29:40,270
General Nan

524
00:29:40,910 --> 00:29:41,830
and Mr. Xi

525
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:44,110
are on the same side as us,

526
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:46,590
everything shall be forgotten.

527
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:54,430
Judging from the current situation,

528
00:29:54,430 --> 00:29:55,510
it's hard

529
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:57,800
for us to choose otherwise.

530
00:29:58,910 --> 00:30:00,510
Mr. Xi, you're a smart man.

531
00:30:00,910 --> 00:30:02,640
Smart people should be sincere

532
00:30:03,430 --> 00:30:04,710
when making friends.

533
00:30:05,230 --> 00:30:08,310
I sent someone to watch your pleasure boat.

534
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:09,830
They said

535
00:30:10,150 --> 00:30:11,230
your attendant

536
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,790
called you 'my lord'.

537
00:30:15,870 --> 00:30:17,030
My lord.

538
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:20,790
What kind of lord are you?

539
00:30:24,470 --> 00:30:26,630
If you don't reveal your identity,

540
00:30:27,650 --> 00:30:29,520
things might look bad for you.

541
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:43,990
Those young people from Lanna Village

542
00:30:43,990 --> 00:30:45,700
who were forced away by you.

543
00:30:46,030 --> 00:30:47,630
Those poor children who died

544
00:30:48,710 --> 00:30:50,970
and the elderly who have no one to rely on.

545
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:53,510
Do you dare to reveal your identity to them?

546
00:30:57,910 --> 00:31:00,110
A bunch of low-life profiteers like you

547
00:31:00,870 --> 00:31:02,130
have no right to ask me.

548
00:31:02,390 --> 00:31:04,100
Since we're not friends,

549
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:05,590
today,

550
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:06,990
you'll die here!

551
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:38,150
My lords,

552
00:32:38,990 --> 00:32:40,070
do you think

553
00:32:40,130 --> 00:32:41,850
you can leave Heman?

554
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,500
We don't have to leave.

555
00:32:44,030 --> 00:32:45,490
We just need to arrest you.

556
00:33:02,870 --> 00:33:04,660
How dare you try to

557
00:33:04,870 --> 00:33:06,870
assassinate an imperial official?

558
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:07,720
You...

559
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:09,790
You set me up!

560
00:33:10,100 --> 00:33:11,760
Didn't you do the same before?

561
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:26,100
The Moqi family profited off Zornia.

562
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:29,230
I'll investigate according to the law.

563
00:33:30,150 --> 00:33:31,830
In order to protect herself,

564
00:33:32,390 --> 00:33:34,430
Moqi confessed that the Heman county magistrate,

565
00:33:34,430 --> 00:33:35,430
Tumen family, and

566
00:33:35,750 --> 00:33:37,950
the county lieutenant, Gongye family,

567
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:39,470
received bribes

568
00:33:39,820 --> 00:33:42,150
and had been secretly supporting the Moqi family.

569
00:33:42,150 --> 00:33:43,630
Tumen and Gongye

570
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,400
refused to plead guilty.

571
00:33:46,270 --> 00:33:47,730
Furious, Moqi personally

572
00:33:48,230 --> 00:33:49,590
killed Tumen.

573
00:33:50,150 --> 00:33:52,150
Under the order of the Emperor,

574
00:33:52,430 --> 00:33:54,160
I've detained Moqi and Gongye.

575
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,150
The trial will be held on another day!

576
00:33:56,150 --> 00:33:58,830
Bravo! Bravo!

577
00:33:59,190 --> 00:34:03,190
Bravo!

578
00:34:03,990 --> 00:34:07,070
Bravo!

579
00:34:09,870 --> 00:34:11,620
They called the shots for so many years.

580
00:34:11,620 --> 00:34:12,590
They must have never thought that

581
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:13,770
they would suffer defeat

582
00:34:13,770 --> 00:34:15,100
in their own territory.

583
00:34:17,310 --> 00:34:19,170
How was the General's Residence?

584
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:20,150
As you expected,

585
00:34:20,150 --> 00:34:21,560
I've handled things there.

586
00:34:21,560 --> 00:34:22,510
Madam and Miss Yan

587
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:23,630
are safe and sound.

588
00:34:23,790 --> 00:34:24,390
My lord,

589
00:34:24,670 --> 00:34:26,480
your plan of capturing the leader first

