Dr. Yan,

608
00:35:26,139 --> 00:35:27,150
what is Mr. Xi's

609
00:35:27,310 --> 00:35:28,400
real identity?

610
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,390
How can General be at ease

611
00:35:30,390 --> 00:35:31,520
