612
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:33,440
I don't know.

613
00:35:33,910 --> 00:35:34,580
But he must be someone

614
00:35:34,580 --> 00:35:35,710
who can protect you.

615
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:38,050
You don't know?

616
00:35:40,470 --> 00:35:42,110
Don't you love each other?

617
00:35:48,430 --> 00:35:49,950
It's a brief thing.

618
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:51,150
I was just

619
00:35:51,750 --> 00:35:52,990
passing by

620
00:35:53,310 --> 00:35:54,950
without real attachment.

621
00:35:57,310 --> 00:35:58,230
I'm different.

622
00:35:58,990 --> 00:36:00,390
I swore to God

623
00:36:01,180 --> 00:36:03,040
to never be apart from my husband.

624
00:36:03,470 --> 00:36:04,630
Alright.

625
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:08,320
Madam.

626
00:36:09,890 --> 00:36:11,090
Speaking of leaving,

627
00:36:11,710 --> 00:36:13,510
I have a request.

628
00:36:14,670 --> 00:36:15,600
Please go ahead.

629
00:36:15,990 --> 00:36:16,870
We're friends.

630
00:36:16,990 --> 00:36:17,830
I'll complete

631
00:36:17,990 --> 00:36:18,910
your request.

632
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:21,080
