633
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:23,340
Our tribe is known for its snake legends.

634
00:36:23,590 --> 00:36:24,710
The magical medicine

635
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:26,390
is used to cure snake venom.

636
00:36:27,070 --> 00:36:28,470
To cure snake venom only?

637
00:36:31,180 --> 00:36:33,180
This medicine can cure all poisons,

638
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,800
