661
00:38:11,910 --> 00:38:12,770
What about you?

662
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:15,000
When are you leaving?

663
00:38:19,470 --> 00:38:20,600
After the full moon.

664
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:23,330
You haven't entered

665
00:38:23,330 --> 00:38:24,730
the general's study yet.

666
00:38:24,990 --> 00:38:26,320
You're leaving so soon?

667
00:38:28,590 --> 00:38:30,190
I'm not going there anymore.

668
00:38:31,030 --> 00:38:32,620
Aren't you looking for your item anymore?

669
00:38:32,620 --> 00:38:33,390
No.

670
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:38,250
Then why did you come back to Heman?

671
00:38:39,390 --> 00:38:40,150
Yeah.

672
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:42,710
Why did I come back here?

673
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,110
Forget it.

674
00:38:48,750 --> 00:38:50,750
At least I witnessed a good show

675
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:52,400
without dying.

676
00:38:53,990 --> 00:38:54,590
By the way,

677
00:38:56,750 --> 00:38:58,280
